    "Developing multimodal interfaces that cater to diverse communication channels, such as visual, auditory, or tactile, can enhance accessibility.",
    "Additionally, leveraging natural language processing techniques to support multiple languages and incorporating assistive technologies can improve inclusivity.",
    "6) Stakeholder Collaboration and Post-Event Analysis: Scientific Challenge: Facilitating effective collaboration among stakeholders and conducting comprehensive post-event analysis to understand the long-term consequences of hazards.",
